    slug: "masnoon-namaz-aur-roz-marha-ki-duain-12x17",
    description: `Masnoon Namaz aur Roz Marha ki Duain is a large-format Islamic reference book produced in a generous 12x17 inch size that presents the essential daily prayers, supplications, and acts of worship in a format designed for easy reading and display. This oversized edition is particularly well suited for use in homes, classrooms, mosques, and madrasahs where the text needs to be visible from a distance or where multiple readers may benefit from a single copy. The book contains a carefully curated collection of the prophetic supplications (du'as and azkar) that cover every significant moment of a Muslim's daily life and worship routine. The section on Salah (prayer) includes the supplications recited before, during, and after the five daily prayers, the du'as for seeking forgiveness after prayer, the tasbihat, and the specific supplications recommended by Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him) for various occasions. The daily supplications section covers morning and evening azkar, the du'a before sleeping and upon waking, supplications for eating and drinking, du'as for entering and leaving the home, prayers for travelling, and supplications for wearing new clothes, among many others. The "roz marha ki duain" portion focuses on the prayers and remembrances that should be part of a Muslim's daily routine, organising them by the time of day so that readers can establish a consistent practice of remembering Allah throughout their waking hours. Each supplication is presented in clear Arabic script with Urdu translation, and the large format ensures that even those with limited Arabic reading ability can follow along comfortably. The generous page size also means there is ample white space, which reduces eye strain and makes the book pleasant to read for extended periods. This edition is particularly valuable for teachers who wish to display the text for their students, for elderly readers who benefit from larger print, and for families who want to place the book in a prominent location in their home as a reminder to engage in daily supplication. The durable construction ensures that this large-format reference will withstand regular use in group settings.`,
    metaDescription: "Masnoon Namaz aur Roz Marha ki Duain 12x17 is a large-format Urdu prayer book with daily supplications for Salah, morning, and evening."
